dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Shows municipal, village, concession, pum cheme boundaries, military barracks and depots, cemeteries, qubba, wadis, railways, and roads. "Topo no. S.881-52." "Note; The detail of this sheet is compiled from cadastral, town and topographical surveys adjusted to triangulation stations. Other information is added from air photographs."
